</TABLE></P>
<P>MARCH. The fir&s;t ten days were dry and agreeable; the re&s;t in general rainy, with boi&s;terous northerly winds towards the end. Atmo&s;phere loaded with vapour.</P>
<P>Rainy days, 11, 14, 15, 16, 22, 24, 25, 27, 28, 29 .. 26 ...</P>
