</TABLE></P>
<P>APRIL&mdash;Was in general dry, but ex|ce&s;&s;ively windy from the ea&s;tward.</P>
<P>Rainy days, 14, 30 .... 19, 23, 24, 25, 26 ..</P>
<P><TABLE>
<ROW>
<CELL ROWS="2">Wind,</CELL>
