<CELL>Ther. H. 85</CELL>
<CELL ROWS="2">M. 81 1/30</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
<CELL>27 days Ea&s;terly.</CELL>
<CELL>L. 80</CELL>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
</ROW>
</TABLE></P>
<P>MAY&mdash;Was generally rainy, with boi&s;|terous gales from N. E. and E. Atmo&s;phere loaded with vapour, and frequently hot and &s;uffocating. Towards the end of the month two earthquakes, and &s;ome thunder and lightning.</P>
<P>Rainy days, 1, 2, 3, 4, 24, 25, 26 ... 5, 6, 9, 10, 11, 14, 15, 16, 20, 21, 22, 23 ..</P>
<P><TABLE>
