<ROW>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
<CELL>3 days calm.</CELL>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
</ROW>
</TABLE></P>
<P><PB N="64" REF="035302_0079_1002186C06019900">
JUNE. This month was frequently wet, warm, and &s;qually, particularly about the middle, with &s;ome thunder and lightning.</P>
<P>Rainy days, 1, 4, 5, 10, 11, 16, 21, 30 ... 6, 7, 8, 17, 18, 20, 22, 23, 24, 27 ..</P>
<P><TABLE>
<ROW>
<CELL ROWS="2">Wind,</CELL>
<CELL>1 day Northerly.</CELL>
<CELL>Ther. H. 87</CELL>
<CELL ROWS="2">M. 84/530</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
<CELL>29 days Ea&s;terly.</CELL>
<CELL>L. 81</CELL>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
</ROW>
</TABLE></P>
<P>JULY. For the mo&s;t part rainy, calm, and &s;ultry, with frequently thick fog.</P>
<P>Rainy days, 8, 11, 14 ... 4, 9, 10, 12, 15, 16, and from 21 to 31 ..</P>
<P><TABLE>
<ROW>
<CELL ROWS="2">Wind,</CELL>
