<CELL ROWS="2">M. 84 21/31</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
<CELL>28 days Ea&s;terly.</CELL>
<CELL>L. 84</CELL>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
</ROW>
</TABLE></P>
<P>AUGUST. Few days of this month were rainy. The weather particularly at the beginning and towards the end, was re|markably dry, calm, and &s;ultry, with a great deal of thunder and lightning, unaccom|panied with rain.</P>
<P>Rainy days, 6, 10, 25, 26 ... Therm. on the 24th, 88; on the 26th, 78.</P>
<P><TABLE>
