<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
</ROW>
</TABLE></P>
<P>NOVEMBER. This month was generally rainy al&s;o, and &s;ometimes extremely tem|pe&s;tuous. The low lands were often inun|dated.</P>
<P>Rainy days all, except 19, 20, 21 ...</P>
