</ROW>
</TABLE></P>
<P><PB N="66" REF="035302_0081_1002186F34C8A260">
DECEMBER. Former part of the month dry and plea&s;ant, with ea&s;terly winds; latter part extremely rainy and &s;tormy, with &s;outherly winds.</P>
<P>No account taken of the rainy days.</P>
