<P>AUGUST. Very little rain fell during this month; but the atmo&s;phere was ge|nerally exce&s;&s;ively clo&s;e, &s;ultry, and loaded with vapour. The winds were very va|riable; but for the mo&s;t part a calm. Some thunder and lightning.</P>
